  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Hypothesis: the hyponatremia of multiple myeloma (m.m.)is true and not pseudohyponatremia by
      using the stewart approach to acid - base interpretation, would like to show that the
      positive charged m- proteins produced in m.m.result in true hyponatremia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
